Package model

Class DatabaseLists

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.DatabaseLists
  • public class DatabaseLists
extends java.lang.Object
    the static DatabaseLists class - holds all static local observablelists that mirror the MySql databases as well as filtered lists for searching and lists used in reports.
